member.name: TfCandidateResult
member.summary: Elements of the TfCandidateResult enumeration are used with the method to specify the result of a reconversion operation performed on a given candidate string.

member.name: TfCandidateResult.CAND_FINALIZED
member.summary: The candidate string has been selected and accepted. The previous text should be replaced with the specified candidate.

member.name: TfCandidateResult.CAND_SELECTED
member.summary: The candidate string has been selected, but the selection is not yet final.

member.name: TfCandidateResult.CAND_CANCELED
member.summary: The reconversion operation has been canceled.
